data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value:
Thanks to everyone that helped SA-MP by contributing to the SA-MP Wikipedia, without you, this program could never have existed. All of the programming and layout of the program was done by JaTochNietDan.
Thanks to StrikenKid for taking the time and effort to record all of the sounds you hear in the sound section of this program, it was a great contribution.
Thanks to Peter for contributing the vehicle images and the skin images.
Thanks to Mike for the weapon icon images.
The pickup images, weapon images and weather images were taken by JaTochNietDan in SA-MP.
Finally, thanks to everyone who downloaded this program, and supported the hard work that was put into creating it for the SA-MP community. If you have any bugs, suggestions or problems, please email me at JaTochNietDan@live.com.
